Name: Rocket Jumper
About the game: Rocket Jumper is a VR FPS game. You can move only with the recoil of an explosion and explore a dungeon. It's time to kill monsters, raise your stats, and explore deeper. How far can you explore by relying on rockets? ---controller---- This game is a VR game and cannot be played with a mouse or keyboard. Currently, the only VR devices identified are Oculus.
